Improve the Shopping Experience with an Add-to-Cart Success Message

Let customers know they’ve successfully added an item to their cart so that they can continue shopping. The add-to-cart success toast requires no action from your customer, allowing them to continue their shopping experience uninterrupted.

Where: This change applies to B2B and D2C Commerce in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

How: This feature is included by default when creating a store. If you have an existing store, republish your site to add the toast message.
title: Improving Cart Experience in Salesforce Commerce
